description:
Dean and Manny have both been with us for a while now, and we thought they should finally meet…and what better way to get acquainted than to be naked in a bathtub together?

“That’s just how we do it here!” Dean proclaimed.

They got really comfortable with each other pretty fast, so it didn’t take long for them to want to get out of the tub and get to the fucking!
title: Dean & Manny: Bareback
